    {
      "id": "document:docs/plans/2026-06-18-electron-ui-design.md",
      "type": "document",
      "name": "2026-06-18-electron-ui-design.md",
      "filePath": "docs/plans/2026-06-18-electron-ui-design.md",
      "summary": "Electron 桌面应用 UI 设计文档，涵盖问题陈述、架构设计、页面结构（仪表盘/客户导入/背调/邮件工坊/发送队列/设置）、数据流和关键设计决策。",
      "tags": ["ui-design", "documentation", "electron", "architecture"],
      "complexity": "moderate"
    },
    {
      "id": "file:electron/main.js",
      "type": "file",
      "name": "main.js",
      "filePath": "electron/main.js",
      "summary": "Electron 主进程入口文件，负责窗口创建、系统托盘、IPC 通信（客户数据导入、飞书多维表格集成、背调状态管理、报告列表、邮件发送队列、设置持久化）及批量邮件发送引擎。",
      "tags": ["entry-point", "electron", "ipc-handler", "email-sending", "main-process"],
      "complexity": "complex",
      "languageNotes": "使用 Electron ipcMain.handle 模式实现近 1700 行 IPC 处理器，集成飞书多维表格 API、XLSX 解析，通过 Node.js https 模块实现代理 TLS 连接用于 SMTP 发送。"
    },
    {
      "id": "file:electron/preload.js",
      "type": "file",
      "name": "preload.js",
      "filePath": "electron/preload.js",
      "summary": "Electron 预加载脚本，通过 contextBridge 向渲染进程安全暴露主进程 API（文件导入、数据加载、配置读写、背调操作、发送控制）。",
      "tags": ["electron", "preload", "context-bridge", "ipc-proxy"],
      "complexity": "simple"
    },
    {
      "id": "file:electron/renderer/app.js",
      "type": "file",
      "name": "app.js",
      "filePath": "electron/renderer/app.js",
      "summary": "Electron 渲染进程核心应用逻辑（1755 行），涵盖仪表盘、客户导入、联系人管理、背调查看与轮询、邮件模板工坊（树形结构编辑、句库组装、预览）、发送队列管理及设置自动保存的完整前端实现。",
      "tags": ["electron", "renderer", "ui-logic", "template-engine", "email-composer"],
      "complexity": "complex",
      "languageNotes": "纯 vanilla JavaScript 实现的 SPA，使用 DOM 操作完成页面切换、Markdown 渲染、模板树形编辑和队列管理，无前端框架依赖。包含多语言邮件组装逻辑（西/葡/英）。"
    },
